    "question_id" : 6623161,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>javac command does not follow a recursive compilation process, so you have either specify each directory when running command, or provide a text file with directories you want to include:</p>\n\n<pre><code>javac -classpath \"${CLASSPATH}\" @java_sources.txt\n</code></pre>\n"
