    "question_id" : 6623161,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I've been using this in an Xcode JNI project to recursively build my test classes:</p>\n\n<pre><code>find ${PROJECT_DIR} -name \"*.java\" -print | xargs javac -g -classpath ${BUILT_PRODUCTS_DIR} -d ${BUILT_PRODUCTS_DIR}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
