    "question_id" : 6623161,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In the usual case where you want to compile your whole project you can simply supply javac with your main class and let it compile all required dependencies:</p>\n\n<p><code>javac -sourcepath . path/to/Main.java</code></p>\n"
